<template>
<v-container>
	<v-row v-for="(timePeriods, index) in periodsInThrees" :key="index">
		<v-col cols="12" md="6" color="purple" v-for="(period, index) in timePeriods" :key="index">
			<time-periods  :header="period.header" :subtopics="period.subtopics" />
		</v-col>
	</v-row>
</v-container>
</template>



<script>
// @ is an alias to /src
import timePeriods from '@/components/TimePeriods.vue'
export default {
	name:'Home',
	components: { 
		timePeriods //translated to time-periods tage
	},
	data() { 
		return {
			timePeriods: [
				{header: "Time Period 1",
				// subtopics: ['Buddhism', 'Mongol Empire', 'Middle Ages', 'Aztecs']
				subtopics:[ 
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"}
					]
				}, 
				{header: "Time Period 2",
				// subtopics: ['African Kingdoms', 'Islamic Empires', 'Renaissance', 'North American Colonies']
				subtopics:[ 
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"}
					]
				}, 
				{header: "Time Period 3",
					subtopics:[ 
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"},
						{img:"logo.png", name: 'American Rev', url: "/Topics"}
					]
				}
			]
		}
	},
	computed:{
		periodsInThrees() {
			return this._.chunk(this.timePeriods, 2);
		}
	}
}
</script>
